data.description: This charming country-style home is nestled on a peaceful oversized lot. This residence exudes warmth, character, and plenty of charm. First, you'll be greeted by a covered front porch adorned with swings, inviting you to relax. Step inside to discover a space of comfort and functionality. The kitchen is a true highlight, featuring a decorated aluminum tile ceiling, wood floors, and ample counter space for all your culinary desires. The cozy family room provides a welcoming atmosphere, while the dining area offers a lovely space for gatherings with loved ones. Step outside to discover a backyard oasis. The covered screened-in back porch is perfect for enjoying the outdoors while staying protected from the elements. The flagstone, decking and fire pit area with seating adds a touch of elegance, creating a serene space for relaxation. The covered grilling area is ideal for hosting barbecues and outdoor gatherings. This home is all this and so much more. Come see for yourself.
